ğŸ§  Tips for Interview
Always mention BST property â‡’ bounded recursion â€” itâ€™s key to optimize from O(NÂ²) to O(N).

Explain why no partitioning or searching is needed â€” just boundaries.

Add a dry run and sketch tree structure when explaining.

You can remember this as:
ğŸ‘‰ â€œUse upper bound for preorder, lower bound for postorder.â€

âœ… Final Thoughts
