âš¡ Space Optimization Tip
If interviewer restricts extra O(N) space:

You can avoid hashmap by doing a linear search in inorder each time (but O(NÂ²) time).

Usually, interviewers accept the O(N) hashmap version since itâ€™s optimal.

ğŸ§© Pattern Recognition
Problem	Traversals Given	Strategy
105. Preorder + Inorder	Root first	Build from start of preorder
106. Inorder + Postorder	Root last	Build from end of postorder
1008. Preorder â†’ BST	Preorder only	Use upper bound trick
Postorder â†’ BST	Postorder only	Use lower bound trick

ğŸ’¡ Trick to Remember
Given Traversals	Root Position	Build Direction
Preorder + Inorder	Root first â†’ from start	Left â†’ Right
Postorder + Inorder	Root last â†’ from end	Right â†’ Left

Mnemonic:

â€œPre â†’ start from front,
Post â†’ start from back.â€

